      "file_path": "/COMMIT_MSG",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 11,
      "message": "Yep, we agree ;)\nNow the issue is, that we ouldn`t find an identity for the so-moniotring in the AAF configuration. If this identity was present with AAF, we`d clearly go for certInitializer.\n\nNow, we`d be rebasing this one, based on gerrit 111328, if it would be possible to use certInitializer, we`d immediately go for it.\n\nOtherwise, we`d have to stay with this apporach, unless we find a way to add new app identities to AAF.",
      "author": {
