      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 29,
      "message": "Sylvain, please note this is contained in override.yaml which \nis exchanged with yaml contained in so-monitoring spring app.\nThe \"nature\" of this config is the same like in i.e bpmn-infra\nor adapters, which also have passwords in override.yaml file.\nThis password is used to access to so-monitoring by human operator\n- it will be described in SO RTD.\n\nFor now, I'm not sure how to \"inject\" secret into file used as\na data into config map. Now It is just moved config to values.yaml \nbut logically it is the same. If you have any hints, I'm open for them. \n\nTaking into account above, and gating results seemed to be fine, I've ticked\nit as \"Resolved\".",
